** About us **

We are an online/Retal business supplying health, aged care & sports
performance markets. We market and distribute a wide variety of products from
local and international suppliers. Having been in business for over 20 years
we are continually evolving to meet the demands of the market and our
customers. We are a small team of 8 that is always looking to improve and
develop the business. Please send cover letter telling us why you think you
would be a good addition to our team.

** Qualifications & experience **

  * Customer Service Experience Preferred but not essential. 
  * Excellent communication and customer service skills 
  * Intermediate Computer skills in MS Outlook and MS Office (Word, excel) 
  * Positive “can do attitude”, reliable, good work ethic and the ultimate multitasker 
  * Ability to work on your own and in a team environment 
  * Attention to detail 
  * Eagerness to learn 
  * Interest/Qualifications in Healthcare/Sports Science would be beneficial. 

** Tasks & responsibilities **

  * Primary contact for all customers across multiple channels, including email, phone, live chat and Social Media 
  * Provide product and pricing information to customers 
  * Resolve customer issues in a prompt and professional manner 
  * Assist with Social Media and Digital Marketing Activities 
  * Assist with product updates and content on our websites 
  * Ensure website images, content and pricing are accurate and up to date 

** Benefits **

  * Monday - Friday 
  * 9am - 5pm 
  * Lots of Variety 
  * Opportunity to learn all facets of an ecommerce/wholesale business 
  * Lot's of potential growth/options as business continues to grow 
  * Small family business 

